-- 01_approved_returns.sql
```sql
CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE approved_returns AS
SELECT DISTINCT ON (r.item_id)
    r.item_id,
    r.return_id
FROM returns r
WHERE r.status = 'approved'
ORDER BY r.item_id, r.return_date DESC;
```

-- 02_return_rates_by_category.sql
```sql
SELECT
    COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN ar.item_id IS NOT NULL THEN oi.quantity END), 0) AS total_items_returned,
    ROUND(
        COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN ar.item_id IS NOT NULL THEN oi.quantity END), 0)::DECIMAL
        / NULLIF(SUM(oi.quantity), 0),
        4
    ) AS return_rate
FROM order_items oi
JOIN products p ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON c.category_id = p.category_id
LEFT JOIN approved_returns ar ON ar.item_id = oi.item_id
GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized')
ORDER BY return_rate DESC;
